  "notes": [
    "AArch64 model v1: covers Cortex-A class integer, load/store, branch, FP, and NEON opcodes.",
    "Cost ratios follow the same relative scale as x86-64 (ALU=1.0, load=2.0, FP=2.8, call=3.0).",
    "Expand alias table from -mllvm -debug-only=isel traces on target hardware for production use.",
    "The pass is architecture-agnostic at the C++ level; target selection is via the JSON model path."
